title: Finite State Raises $20 Million to Grow Software Supply Chain Security Business
description:

title: German Authorities Shut Down Online Marketplace for Drugs, Data and Cybercrime Services
description:
German authorities took down the Nemesis Market, a major online marketplace for drugs, cybercrime services and stolen credit card data.
